{"tid":323480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解散立會重選?","createTime":"2017-07-15T15:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T16:43:53.000Z","uid":119277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57f607f5b7cff5d695a2769e2774943925b524aa","tid":323480,"uid":119277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:51:39.000Z","msg":"基本法第五十條「&hellip;立法會拒絕通過&hellip;或其他重要法案，經協商仍不能取得一致意見，行政長官可解散立法會」<br />\n<br />\nCE可否話佢覺得36億教育撥款係「重要法案」？<br />\n咁19號過唔到算唔算「拒絕通過」？<br />\n<br />\n話晒十年樹木百年樹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第七十條話解散咗三個月內要重選，<br />\n十月佢又可以宣讀施政報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53c2b85452beb5c2dbc7d865318007ec39b1d7e","tid":323480,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"唔會，政府唔會俾你翻盤"}]}